lyx2ebook by Will Tang, copyright 2010 under the GPL version 3
===============================================================================
A simple LyX file to eBook converter.

===============================================================================
Uses Lepl parser to parse LyX file:

http://www.acooke.org/lepl/

Lepl by Andrew Cooke, copyright 2009-2010 under the Mozilla Public Licence 
and the Lesser Gnu Public Licence. The documentation is licensed under
the Gnu Free Documentation Licence. 


Includes a lightly modified RP parser module, original web site:

http://lparis45.free.fr/rp.html

RP by L. Paris, copyright 2008 under the GNU General Public License
